FBIS4-7034 "dreas080_c_94026" FBIS-EAS-94-080 Daily Report 26 Apr 1994 North Korea Vietnamese Party Delegation Continues Visit Vietnamese Party Delegation Continues Visit Kim Il-song Meets Delegation SK2604110094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1035 GMT 26 Apr 94 SK2604110094 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 26 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song today received the visiting delegation of the Communist Party of Vietnam headed by secretary of its Central Committee Hong Ha. Present there were Secretary Hwang Chang-yop and Vice Department Director Kim Yang-kon of the C.C., the Workers' Party of Korea and Vietnamese Ambassador to Korea Duong Chinh Thuc. President Kim Il-song conversed with the guests in a cordial and friendly atmosphere.
